 of excited state surfaces is also\nnumerically examined for species like H$_2$, NH$_3$, C$_2$H$_6$ and LiH in\nextended basis sets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Aug 2019 21:44:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-14"}
