mplete system demonstrates that StateLens successfully enables\nblind users to access otherwise inaccessible dynamic touchscreens.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Aug 2019 03:23:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-21"}
