neutrino sources in the Southern Sky is\nreported here. No significant evidence of cosmic neutrino sources is found and\nflux upper limits from the various searches are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Aug 2019 15:42:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-21"}
